description:
During the course you'll learn how to install a SAP Business Objects BI 4.1 system for free.

The course is aimed at anyone interested in learning SAP Business Objects. Once you've installed and configured your SAP Business Objects system you can use it as your own personal development system.

In the course i'll take you through the complete installation process from start to finish.

From experience I know that you can encounter issues during the installation of the Business Objects server. If you need help, please leave a comment and i'll try to help you as much as possible.

Enjoy!
title: Build a Free SAP Business Objects BI Trial System
